        Constructor for the MainThread.
        Parameters:
        threadPool - To pass the existing threadpool to the mainthread.
        errorLabel - To pass the errorLabel so the mainthread can show errors.
        loginButton - To pass the login button so the mainthread can disable/enable it.
        host - The hostname/ip the client will connect to.
        port - The port the client uses to connect.
        name - The username the client has chosen.
